OL,5, A scheme that offers discounts on bills
OL,6, for households who cut peak-time       
OL,7, electricity use will be triggered on   
OL,8, Monday as the UK's cold snap continues.
OL,10,FNational Grid ESO said it would        
OL,11,Factivate the scheme, which has only    
OL,12,Fbeen used in tests until now, between  
OL,13,F17:00 and 18:00 GMT.                   
OL,15,FIt has also asked for three coal-fired 
OL,16,Fgenerators to be warmed up.            
OL,18,FNational Grid ESO said the measures    
OL,19,Fwere "precautionary" and it did not    
OL,20,Fmean electricity supplies were at risk.
